T1  - Taxation and Income Distribution Dynamics in a Neoclassical Growth Model
AU  - GARCÍA-PEÑALOSA, CECILIA
AU  - TURNOVSKY, STEPHEN J.
Y1  - 2011/12/01
PY  - 2011
